How to summarize OTU-table using atlas-utils

#0. prerequisite

   atlas-utils
   zotu_table.txt, QIIME table format

1. column summary

   calculate OTU counts and Tags counts.
      
      atlas-utils summary  zotu_table.txt


2. row summary

   calculate OTU tags number in all samples
      
      atlas-utils summary  zotu_table.txt
